source.name: Softwood Lumber Subsidies Report
source.description: A report generated by Commerce and submitted to Congress every 180 days pursuant to the Softwood Lumber Act of 2008, detailing any subsidies, including stumpage subsidies, provided by countries exporting softwood lumber or softwood lumber products to the United States.
